# <Project> — UI Style Guide: embedded

**Per-kind дополнение к `ui-style-guide-base.md`.** Правила для встраиваемых устройств — smartwatch, ring (Oura, Whoop), IoT панели, automotive HMI, e-ink reader, smart home displays, кассовые терминалы. Constraints: малый дисплей, ограниченная память, специфичный input (rotary / hardware buttons / capacitive / voice), низкое энергопотребление.

Часто работает в паре с companion app (`native-mobile`) и backend (`backend`).

---

## 1. Платформенные группы

Каждая платформа — свои capabilities и conventions:

| Платформа | OS / Stack | Display | Input |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Apple Watch** | watchOS / SwiftUI | OLED 41-49mm | Digital Crown + touch + voice (Siri) |
| **Wear OS** | Wear OS / Compose for Wear | OLED 40-45mm | Touch + crown (some) + voice |
| **Garmin** | Connect IQ / MonkeyC | MIP / OLED varies | Buttons + touch (некоторые) |
| **Pebble-like / open** | Rebble / PebbleOS / custom | E-ink / MIP | Buttons primary |
| **Smart ring** | Custom RTOS | None (LED only) | Gestures via sensors |
| **E-ink reader** | Kindle / Kobo / Onyx | E-ink 6-13" | Touch + buttons |
| **Automotive HMI** | Android Automotive / QNX / custom | LCD 7-15" | Touch + voice + hardware controls |
| **Smart speaker** | Voice OS (Alexa, custom) | None / small display | Voice primary |
| **IoT panel / home display** | ESP32 / Raspberry Pi custom | LCD 2-7" | Touch + buttons |
| **POS / terminal** | Embedded Linux / custom | LCD 7-15" | Touch primary |
| **Microcontroller с LCD** | bare metal / FreeRTOS / Zephyr | OLED / TFT small | Buttons + rotary |

---

## 2. Constraints first

Embedded дизайн — **constraint-driven**. Каждая ось определяет дизайн:

### 2.1. Display constraints

- **Размер:** 1-7 inch typical; редко больше
- **Resolution:** низкое (160×80 на watch чипах до 480×480 на современных watches)
- **Color depth:** монохромный (e-ink), greyscale, 16-bit color, full 24-bit color
- **Refresh rate:** 1 fps (e-ink) до 60 fps (modern watches)
- **Persistent:** e-ink / MIP не drains battery; OLED / LCD — drains

Design implication: minimal information density, чётко обозначенная иерархия, large тапабельные зоны.

### 2.2. Memory / CPU constraints

- RAM: kilobytes до low MB (microcontrollers); GBs только в premium devices
- Storage: limited; assets compressed
- CPU: slow, не parallel; UI rendering на main thread
- **Никаких** JavaScript-heavy stacks в low-end embedded

### 2.3. Power constraints

- Battery life — часто primary metric (smartwatch 24h+, ring 7d+, sensors months)
- Минимизировать redraw (особенно e-ink — каждый refresh costly)
- Deep sleep / wake-on-event design
- Connectivity sparing (BLE > WiFi battery-wise)
- CPU clock scaling

### 2.4. Input modalities

| Modality | Где | Дизайн implications |
|---|---|---|
| Touch (capacitive) | Watch / panels | Touch targets ≥ 9mm physical размер |
| Hardware buttons | Garmin / cheap devices / panels | Limited (2-5 buttons typical); каждая кнопка multiple actions через short/long press |
| Rotary encoder / Digital Crown | Apple Watch / некоторые devices | Scroll + zoom + selection |
| Voice | Smart speakers / watches | Conversational, не command-line |
| Gestures (accelerometer) | Rings / fitness | Tap / shake / wrist flick / sleep detection |
| Haptic feedback | Output channel | Confirm tactile без display |
| Sound / beep | Output | Notifications для devices without display |

---

## 3. Visual design — minimal information density

### 3.1. Информация на экране

**Principle:** один primary message + один secondary maximum. Не пытаться втиснуть desktop UI в watch.

Examples:

| Watch face | Primary | Secondary |
|---|---|---|
| Time | 14:23 | (день / battery / steps small) |
| Workout active | Heart rate 142 | (duration / pace small) |
| Notification | Message preview | (sender / time small) |

### 3.2. Типографика

- Большой size для primary info (40-60% display height для key number)
- Sans-serif rounded для legibility на маленьком display
- Variable fonts если platform support
- **Никаких** thin / light weights — нечитаемо на small displays
- High contrast обязательно (см. § 5)

### 3.3. Цвет

- **OLED:** true black background — saves power (pixels off)
- **MIP / e-ink:** monochrome или limited palette — design through size / weight / spacing, не color
- **Color OLED:** still мало цветов — 2-3 brand colors maximum

### 3.4. Icons

- **System icons** где доступны (SF Symbols для watchOS, Material Symbols для Wear)
- Размер 24-44pt на watches; 32-64pt на panels
- Filled style чаще читается лучше чем stroke на small displays

### 3.5. Layout patterns

- **List view** — vertical scroll, large rows
- **Card** — one focused item, taps to drill down
- **Status grid** — 2×2 metrics для glanceable info
- **Workout/activity** — single primary metric, swipe для secondary
- **Voice + visual confirmation** — text confirms what voice command did

---

## 4. Input — modality-specific дизайн

### 4.1. Touch на маленьком display

- **Touch targets** ≥ **9mm × 9mm** physical (≈ 44pt on watch retina)
- Spacing между targets ≥ 2mm
- **Гесты:**
  - Tap → primary action
  - Long press → context menu / cancel mode (sparingly)
  - Swipe horizontal → navigation между screens
  - Swipe vertical → scroll
  - **Никаких** complex multi-finger gestures — мало места

### 4.2. Hardware buttons

С limited buttons design — каждая кнопка multi-function:

| Действие | Pattern |
|---|---|
| Short press | Primary action |
| Long press (1-2s) | Secondary / activate / wake |
| Hold (3+s) | Reset / power off (system) |
| Double click | Special action |

**Discoverable:** at first run — onboarding screen объясняет button functions.

### 4.3. Rotary encoder / Digital Crown

- **Rotate** — scroll list / change value
- **Press** — select / activate
- Combined с touch — rotary for fine-tune, touch для coarse

### 4.4. Voice

См. § 6 (отдельная секция).

### 4.5. Sensor input (gestures)

Ring / wristband без display — input через motion:

| Жест | Pattern |
|---|---|
| Tap on device | Acknowledge / dismiss |
| Double tap | Activate |
| Shake | Cancel / wake |
| Wrist flick | Next item |

**Critical:** discoverable через companion app + onboarding.

---

## 5. Accessibility

### 5.1. Visual

- **Large text mode** — поддерживается system-level
- **High contrast** mode (для low-vision)
- **VoiceOver / TalkBack** через watchOS / Wear OS native APIs
- Цвет не единственный носитель (см. base.md § 4.1)

### 5.2. Hearing

- Voice notifications + visual + haptic redundant
- Captions для voice output (если есть display)
- Vibration patterns для разных alert types

### 5.3. Motor

- Voice control как alternative для touch
- Long press timing configurable
- Touch sensitivity adjustable
- Haptic confirmation для button presses

### 5.4. Cognitive

- Минимальные cognitive load — одна вещь на экране
- Стандартные patterns, не custom
- Undo / recovery — где возможно

---

## 6. Voice interfaces (где applicable)

### 6.1. Wake words

- System-provided («Hey Siri», «Hey Google», «Alexa»)
- Custom wake words — рассматриваем только для dedicated devices
- Visual feedback что устройство listens (LED / display icon)

### 6.2. Intent design

- **Conversational**, не command-line — «set timer for ten minutes» а не «timer 10 m»
- **Confirm critical actions** voice + visual («Delete X? Say yes or no.»)
- **Graceful fallback** на «I didn't get that» с подсказкой

### 6.3. Privacy

- LED / display показывает когда mic active — обязательно
- Local processing где возможно (не отправлять каждый wake word в cloud)
- User control над history (delete recordings, opt-out)

---

## 7. Connectivity + sync с companion app

### 7.1. Pairing flow

- BLE pairing через companion app (`native-mobile`)
- Onboarding в companion: scan QR / enter PIN / confirm pairing
- Recovery: re-pair через factory reset device + companion screen

### 7.2. Sync patterns

- **Background sync** — device → phone когда в range
- **Event-driven** — push critical events immediately (HR alert / fall detection)
- **Pull periodically** — non-critical (logs / settings)
- **Offline-first** — device functions standalone, sync when available

### 7.3. Notifications

- Tactile + minimal visual — vibration pattern + glanceable preview
- **Source привязан** — notification specifies sender / topic
- Acknowledge через short tap / single button → dismiss

---

## 8. Loading + feedback (отзывчивость)

### 8.1. Visual feedback

- **Tap acknowledged:** instant visual change (button press state) + haptic
- **Loading > 200ms:** spinner / pulse animation
- **Long operation:** prevent multiple invocations (disabled state)
- **Result:** completed state visible 1-2s before auto-dismiss

### 8.2. Без display

- **Haptic** as primary feedback (single buzz = ack, double buzz = error, long = critical)
- **Sound** if speaker present + user enables
- **LED color/pattern** for status (green = good, red = error, blinking = active)
- Documented in companion app reference

---

## 9. Эффективность пути

См. base.md § 1 (принцип 8). Embedded amplifies:

- 2-3 taps maximum для common actions (start workout, dismiss notification)
- Most-used action — на default screen, не buried
- **Complications / glances** для critical info (no taps needed)
- Voice short-cuts для frequent actions

---

## 10. Frameworks-first для embedded

### 10.1. Watch / wearable

| Platform | Framework |
|---|---|
| Apple Watch | **SwiftUI for watchOS** (default), WatchKit (legacy) |
| Wear OS | **Jetpack Compose for Wear OS** |
| Garmin | Connect IQ SDK (MonkeyC) |
| TicWatch / Wear-OS based | Wear OS frameworks |

### 10.2. IoT / Panel

| Class | Framework |
|---|---|
| ESP32 / similar MCU | **LVGL** (popular UI library для C/C++) |
| ESP32 / SquareLine for visual design | SquareLine Studio |
| Embedded Linux | **Qt for Embedded**, GTK, **Flutter Embedded** |
| Raspberry Pi GUI | Same as Linux desktop (Qt / GTK / Flutter) |
| Touch panel small | **Slint** (modern Rust/C++ UI for embedded) |

### 10.3. Automotive

- Android Automotive (AOSP)
- QNX
- AGL (Automotive Grade Linux)
- Custom HMI frameworks

### 10.4. E-ink

- Kindle SDK (Amazon proprietary)
- Kobo SDK
- Onyx Boox — Android-based; standard Android frameworks (с e-ink considerations)
- Custom — drive controller directly через SPI

---

## 11. Дистрибуция + lifecycle

- **App stores:** App Store (watchOS), Play Store (Wear OS), Garmin Connect IQ Store, etc.
- **Firmware updates:** OTA через companion app
- **Version skew handling:** companion app должен поддерживать old firmware versions
- **End-of-life:** documented support window; security patches до declared EOL

---

## 12. Embedded-specific checklist

В дополнение к `ui-style-guide-base.md` § 7:

- [ ] Display constraints учтены (размер / resolution / refresh / color depth / persistent vs OLED)
- [ ] Memory / CPU budget определён, design fits
- [ ] Battery impact каждой feature оценён
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 9mm physical (если touch interface)
- [ ] Hardware buttons mapped с long-press для secondary actions
- [ ] Onboarding объясняет input modalities (gestures / buttons / voice)
- [ ] Voice intents conversational, не command-line (если voice)
- [ ] Visual feedback что mic / camera active (privacy)
- [ ] Haptic + sound + LED как fallback feedback (если no display)
- [ ] Color не единственный носитель (для monochrome / e-ink critical)
- [ ] Offline-first — device functions без connectivity
- [ ] Companion app pairing flow + recovery
- [ ] Background sync (BLE) battery-efficient
- [ ] OTA firmware update support
- [ ] System theme follow + manual override (где applicable)
- [ ] Accessibility — large text / high contrast / VoiceOver-equivalent
- [ ] EOL / support window declared
